24#define SYS_MAXSYSARGS 8
25
26#undef syscallarg
27#define syscallarg(x) \
28 union { \
29 register_t pad; \
30 struct { x datum; } le; \
31 struct { /* LINTED zero array dimension */ \
32 int8_t pad[ /* CONSTCOND */ \
33 (sizeof (register_t) < sizeof (x)) \
34 ? 0 \
35 : sizeof (register_t) - sizeof (x)]; \
36 x datum; \
37 } be; \
38 }
39
40#undef check_syscall_args
41#define check_syscall_args(call) /*LINTED*/ \
42 typedef char call##_check_args[sizeof (struct call##_args) \
43 <= SYS_MAXSYSARGS * sizeof (register_t) ? 1 : -1];
